SELECT 
  id, 
  title, 
  concat('https://idyoveanwiuwcvgxijtz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/eagle-images/', storage_path) as imageUrl
FROM eagle_images
WHERE 
  title ILIKE '%worm%' OR title ILIKE '%fire%'
  OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM unnest(tags) AS tag WHERE tag ILIKE '%worm%')
  OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM unnest(tags) AS tag WHERE tag ILIKE '%fire%')
ORDER BY created_at DESC, random()
LIMIT 3;
